page.title: 13Industry in Wroxall 1.
page.content: Wroxall timber yard has been open in Wroxall for 2 years. It retails timber.The materials it uses are timber,plywood,hardboard,chipboard and plasterboard.The materials for the factory come from Russia,Canada, Sweden,Romania and Belgium.They sell the timber at the yard in Wroxall. Crowe Electrics has been open in Wroxall for nearly 2 years.The factory makes burglar alarms for cars,boats and caravans.The factory uses electronic parts.The factory changes the materials by putting them in a box and connecting wires.The materials are made in England.They are sold to mail order suppliers,that sell to other electronics company like Crowe's.
